               <msContents>
                  <summary>Asmat Prayers Against Charm, ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መፍትሔ፡ ሥራይ; Net of Solomon, መርበበተ፡ ሰሎሞን፡; Bandlet of Righteousness, ልፋፈ፡ ጽድቅ፡; Asmat Prayer of the Nails of the Cross of Our Lord Jesus Christ, አስማተ፡ ቅንዋተ፡ መስቀሉ፡; Book of Disciples, መጽሐፈ፡ አርድእት፡; Prayer of Our Lady Mary at Golgotha, ጸሎተ፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘሰኔ፡ ጎልጎታ፡; Mystagogia, ትምህርተ፡ ኅቡዓት፡</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝʿǝz</textLang>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" facs="007"/>
